**Overview**

This dashboard displays key statistics and visualizations based on event logs from the CyberArk EPM integration. It includes the top users, policies, products, and logon status; a breakdown of events by type, threat protection action, access target type, access target name, source type, and logon attempt type; along with a time-based event trend line chart and essential details about the event data.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/cyberark_epm/overview)
